# S01-T04: CI/CD Pipeline

## Objective
Set up automatic deployment for Frontend (Vercel) and Backend (Railway/Vercel).

## Acceptance Criteria
- `vercel.json` configured in root/client.
- Automatic deploy on push to `main`.
- Environment variables configured in deployment platforms.

## Steps
1. Connect GitHub repo to Vercel.
2. Configure `vercel.json` rewrites for API.
3. Verify live URL.
